EN: The downstream area of the river consists of many different species of plants and animals.
ZH: 下游的水质因上游的人类活动而受到了污染。
EN: The water quality downstream has been affected by human activities upstream.
ZH: 下游的河段水位较低, 可以容纳更多的降水。
EN: The water level in the downstream section is lower, allowing for more precipitation to be accommodated.
